    (LDP) which aims to develop free, high quality documentation for
    the GNU/Linux operating system. By using an SGML/XML-based
    authoring format (<ulink
    url="http://www.oasis-open.org/docbook/">DocBook</ulink>) many
    different types of output may be generated from a single source,
    including HTML and printable formats, without compromising quality
    or portability across computing platforms.</para>

